Class ModuleTest

java.lang.Object
testframework.BaseTest
business.ModuleTest
public class ModuleTest
extends BaseTest
Test class for the Module entity. Contains unit tests to verify the functionality of Module class methods including getters, course associations, and search/filter operations.
